"Ah'll have t' see fer mahself," he said to Sinesis, mentioning about the CR 
chambers. "Ya don't have to stand guard. Didn't ah tell ya t' go get 
Silverstryke? Go get him!" He could barely stand.

He heard from Mantella, so he replied surly with, "Jus' get inside! Th' 
auto-guns will deal wit' 'em!"
